{"tid":2352304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[日記]一個時下20歲香港年輕人日記","createTime":"2021-01-04T02:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T20:18:41.000Z","uid":200162,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b02bdbcdac49d112c93befef31d494d3ec24319","tid":2352304,"uid":200162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"細細個都寫過日記<br />\n不過因為唔記得左寫/日日太悶無野寫而停咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次想寫日記嘅原因係因為 <br />\n返緊intern 覺得前途好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想寫日記 <br />\n督促自己每日進步 有新野可以寫 可以分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會日日更新<br />\n希望可以每日都記錄到有質素嘅生活<br />\n呢個post會見證住我嘅生活<br />\n見證我嘅成長/浪費嘅光陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nstarting from 04/01/2021"},{"pid":"9e0ab5b42b4299b20a9d7f31c9da5b73202884ea","tid":2352304,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"一定好慘"},{"pid":"835a6cbdc68f1e26f27e6661a8814772e42c00a7","tid":2352304,"uid":200162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0ab5b42b4299b20a9d7f31c9da5b73202884ea","tid":2352304,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"一定好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />預見到會成日寫 <br />\n今日好悶 無咩新野<br />\n所以想做多啲新野<br />\n令個日記 令我嘅人生無咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504b68aab8c4564d5da49d37c5e43fe99fe81c6f","tid":2352304,"uid":200162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"2021-01-04<br />\n扮工時間睇左啲excel片 <br />\n算係學左啲實用嘅工作技能 <br />\n股票小賺 繼續放置play<br />\n唔算好充實但都唔算白費左一日<br />\n算係善用左60%時間"},{"pid":"add09b2c97ed253a4c95d51e8065fa85a2f7cc90","tid":2352304,"uid":293355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01